menawan, menakjubkan,…

42
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,360
…berbakat sastra tak tertandingi…

43
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,080
…dan merupakan wanita
istimewa langka.

44
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:17,910
