Sebenarnya ada dua orang bibi…

49
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:33,920
…bilang Anda berpostur anggun
dan berwajah bulat.

50
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:36,270
Bulat?

51
00:04:39,230 --> 00:04:39,720
Tidak!

52
