berubah dia juga tak tidur.

124
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:34,200
Pukul kepalanya?

125
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,960
Tak ada cara lain lagi.

126
00:10:41,710 --> 00:10:43,030
Tak ada salahnya mencoba.

127
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:44,230
Jing Xin.

128
00:10:48,230 --> 00:10:48,690
Tuan Putri.

129
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:50,210
Sampaikan pesan ke Kediaman Mo.

130
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:53,840
Minta Tuan Muda ke-8
keluar bersamaku besok.

131
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:55,640
